{"tid":768670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【圖輯】樂聲怨聲響咹聲　繼續響徹尖沙嘴海旁","createTime":"2018-08-05T15:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T01:25:30.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"b351782e16e532a59ae5c1589c0bbf5443e5a1b2","tid":768670,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180805/s00001/6694b966ee1d03ddad1b912ec219e9f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180805%2Fs00001%2F6694b966ee1d03ddad1b912ec219e9f7.jpg&h=59f7b451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180805/s00001/669c1ebdf33e10f0125a9787dc8096b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180805%2Fs00001%2F669c1ebdf33e10f0125a9787dc8096b1.jpg&h=5b8f3c10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180805/s00001/669c46780e16c63068ae760cf76838b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180805%2Fs00001%2F669c46780e16c63068ae760cf76838b1.jpg&h=ff087fef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180805/s00001/669c6e8f0a7507df825764ca0dff6ded.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180805%2Fs00001%2F669c6e8f0a7507df825764ca0dff6ded.jpg&h=4116b37a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180805/s00001/669c99e7e7b57e4f1734e06fd49f2e93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180805%2Fs00001%2F669c99e7e7b57e4f1734e06fd49f2e93.jpg&h=58c5334f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180805/s00001/669cc202ce7e4f3cbaaa6456f86a0ffd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180805%2Fs00001%2F669cc202ce7e4f3cbaaa6456f86a0ffd.jpg&h=52c4116a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180805/s00001/669ce96bf253b2f3a2e914d0662750c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180805%2Fs00001%2F669ce96bf253b2f3a2e914d0662750c6.jpg&h=033a8898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180805/s00001/669d11dab04ed694368f463fb0934ce9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180805%2Fs00001%2F669d11dab04ed694368f463fb0934ce9.jpg&h=3a097249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180805/s00001/669d3978dab3b9e984d1e67ebfc7c2c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180805%2Fs00001%2F669d3978dab3b9e984d1e67ebfc7c2c8.jpg&h=97a6b72d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角取消行人專用區後，昔日歌聲喧鬧場面轉到尖沙嘴海旁。天星碼頭這晚再度擠滿表演者和圍觀人士，加上不少人上落船和巴士、進出海港城等，行人路水泄不通，歌聲、埋怨聲和響咹聲，一又次響徹海旁。<br />\n<br />\n記者現場所見，有約10檔歌唱團體表演和跳舞，有人因位置問題爭執。又因檔與檔之間距離很近，多支隊伍不斷提高喇叭聲響；在場警察多次發出勸喻後，他們稍為克制，但未幾又打回原形。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180805/s00001/1533475925745\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180805%2Fs00001%2F1533475925745&d=dgh%2BcIwXMOALXFQC76gWsgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=59d4674e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180805%2Fs00001%2F1533475925745&h=1f3589c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180805/s00001/1533475925745</a>"},{"pid":"43b3ae1b791dfebcb46785a48590325568932a8f","tid":768670,"uid":132587,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:10:50.000Z","msg":"香港係咪真係要搞到咁呀<br />\n發生乜撚野事呀"},{"pid":"e06b5f77a07af5f33fed50109db571bb9ea2167f","tid":768670,"uid":35696,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":